{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"故：在 CORS 头 Access-Control-Allow-Credentials 中预期为 true","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/CORS/Errors/CORSMIssingAllowCredentials","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"理由","title":"理由","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">故：在 CORS 头 Access-Control-Allow-Credentials 中预期设为 true\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"错在了哪儿？","title":"错在了哪儿？","isH3":false,"content":"<p>CORS 请求要求服务器允许使用凭据，但是服务器的 HTTPHeader：Access-Control-Allow-Credentials 标头的值并没有设置为 true。</p>\n<p>想要在客户端解决此问题，请修改代码以不请求使用凭据：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>如果要使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a> 发出请求，请确保没有将 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/withCredentials\" title=\"withCredentials\"><code>withCredentials</code></a> 设置为 true。</li>\n  <li>如果使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events\">Server-sent events</a>，请确保<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource/withCredentials\"><code>EventSource.withCredentials</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>为 false（default）。</li>\n  <li>如果使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API\">Fetch API</a>，请确保<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Request/credentials\"><code>Request.credentials</code></a>为“omit”。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>想要通过更改服务器的配置来消除此错误，请调整服务器的配置以将 Access-Control-Allow-Credentials 标头的值设置为 true。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"更多","title":"更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/CORS/Errors\">CORS errors</a></li>\n  <li>Glossary: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/CORS\">CORS</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/CORS\">CORS introduction</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"理由","id":"理由"},{"text":"错在了哪儿？","id":"错在了哪儿？"},{"text":"更多","id":"更多"}],"summary":"CORS 请求要求服务器允许使用凭据，但是服务器的 HTTPHeader：Access-Control-Allow-Credentials 标头的值并没有设置为 true。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Reason: expected 'true' in CORS header 'Access-Control-Allow-Credentials'","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Reason: expected ‘true’ in CORS header ‘Access-Control-Allow-Credentials’","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/http/cors/errors/corsmissingallowcredentials","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/http/cors/errors/corsmissingallowcredentials/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP","title":"HTTP"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/CORS","title":"跨源资源共享（CORS）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/CORS/Errors","title":"CORS errors"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/CORS/Errors/CORSMIssingAllowCredentials","title":"故：在 CORS 头 Access-Control-Allow-Credentials 中预期为 true"}],"pageTitle":"故：在 CORS 头 Access-Control-Allow-Credentials 中预期为 true - HTTP | MDN","noIndexing":false}}